The draw for the quarter-finals of this season’s UEFA Europa League was conducted in Nyon on Friday. The draw was streamed live on UEFA’s official website from 1.30 pm, Nigerian time. The Europa League quarter-final first and second leg ties will take place on April 7 and 14. Below is Europa League quarter-final draw: Leipzig vs Atalanta Eintracht Frankfurt vs Barcelona West Ham vs Lyon Braga vs Rangers